<section>
    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>The <code>&lt;slide-accept-wc&gt;</code> component creates a slide-to-confirm interaction &mdash; a draggable handle that users slide across a track to confirm an action (like iOS &ldquo;slide to power off&rdquo;). If released early, the handle springs back. Once the threshold is reached, the component activates and fires a <code>slide-accept</code> event.</p>

    <browser-window
